title: [Orcswold, Fields]
description: A scattering of trees mark the edge of the wooded area that bounds the grassy fields to the north, and the twittering of a flock of birds nestled invisibly somewhere in the nearby trees fills the air.  The ground slopes down to the south, leveling into a low windswept moor.

A scattering of trees mark the edge of the wooded area that bounds the grassy fields to the north, and the chirping of crickets nestled invisibly somewhere in the nearby underbrush fills the air.  The ground slopes down to the south, leveling into a low windswept moor.
